title: DJ CHRIS - OLD SCHOOL 2-STEP GARAGE UK MIX (320 KBPS).mp3
description:
This is a 30 minute simple mix that I did of an old school music genre from the UK called 2-step Garage. It's kinda mixed with a few other genres, but it's all good. I like the idea of stepping out of the box, experimenting with various music genres that I have little or no knowledge of whatsoever, doing something totally different from the usual "Reggae, Dancehall & Hip-Hop" mixes which are the majority of Jamaican DJs accustomed route. Let me know what you think. Enjoy!
